    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a phase though. it feels terminal. like the well is actually dry for good. what's the point of even trying to \"find my way\" back to something that clearly isn't there anymore? it just feels like i'm existing in a body that's waiting for a purpose that died years ago.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
